// mealplan app

// landing page greeting user and inviting them to generate a mealplan 
//brief description on how mealplan app works

// step one
// check boxes to select which diet the user follows
// button that takes to the next step

//step two
//checkboxes to select any food intollerances >> nuts, dairy, etc
// if user selects diet that doest not inclue any of the food intollerances then they are eliminated from the list
// button that takes to the next step


// step three
// user is presented checkboxes that allow them to select the amount of days they want the mealplan for
// button that evaluates the mealplan


//step four
// meal plan is presented on page
// with nutritional information for each day that has been generated

// step four provides user with the option to shuffle for more recipes, 'save the day' and build their own week,   and/or print the mealplan

// **STRETCH GOAL** with saving the day the user can also move days around to reorganize their week.